line_1: The Hebrew said, and full of black portent:
line_2: Unhappy man! thy dream from God was sent,

line_1: Fame yet reserv'd is mark'd by this portent;
line_2: This flame, great Jove from high Olympus sent;

line_1: Nor does it claim alone, The Grand Portent
line_2: Foretells the Blessing, and decrees th'Event.
